title: Ep - 174 - JULIET ANGUS FROM LADIES OF LONDON
description:
Juliet Angus is a London based stylist, digital influencer, and appeared on Bravo’s hit show Ladies of London. She talks about how she was cast for the show, how the show changed her life, what castmates she keeps in touch with, and how she has been able to become a successful digital influencer.


Bud Siegel, a retired grandfather reviews the Netflix documentary After Porn Ends, a documentary about the lives and careers of some of the biggest names in the adult entertainment industry after they leave the business.


Jarett Wieselman is a fellow reality tv lover and lives and works in LA. He explains why Real Housewives of Potomac is having one of the best seasons of tv. 


Katie Hamilton appears on Marrying Millions on Lifetime TV, a show that explores whether love and happiness can truly exist between a member of the champagne and caviar set, and someone more accustomed to a life of, say, canned beer and ramen noodles.
